      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength from tensile coupon testing (N=6 per material lot, CV < 3%). Implant geometry from CMM measurements of three production screws and rods; nominal dimensions used with dimensional tolerances propagated as input uncertainty. Input uncertainty quantified and included in E/uval calculation."
    },
    {
